{
  "stem": "210.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And his house was like, you know, they-- he had a lot of connections with Germans, that he worked for them, made them suits, and things like this, for their wives.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- they took me to my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at-- at that time, you know, it-- it wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't take away girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they made-- and they took away men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what-- whoever men they found, they knocked in the night-- in the middle of the night on the door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever men they found, they took 'em away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and from that time, on I-- I worked in the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't remember what they paid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very minimal, but at-- if you worked, they-- you-- they gave you, let's say, more bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave you so much sugar a week, and so much, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was a little, you know, kind of a little better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this went on like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, we tried to sell little things, whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember we had the most beautiful bedspread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, it was from velvet, and it was so gorgeous, you know, for two beds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because at home, we had two beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when we-- this was kind of the last thing that we wanted to give up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because you're-- we're-- we're gonna survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We're gonna need it, and we just-- to have something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we sold that one too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember this-- also that German woman bought.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I don't know if she bought it for herself or-- or she sold it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, so from-- and then I-- I worked in the-- in-- in the shop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then my father got-- got-- this was already in-- in '42.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My father got sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
